<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Photoswipe on Hugo 主題 Stack</title><link>https://demo.stack.cai.im/zh-hant-tw/tags/photoswipe/</link><description>Recent content in Photoswipe on Hugo 主題 Stack</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-hant-tw</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 26 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://demo.stack.cai.im/zh-hant-tw/tags/photoswipe/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>相簿</title><link>https://demo.stack.cai.im/zh-hant-tw/p/image-gallery/</link><pubDate>Mon, 26 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://demo.stack.cai.im/zh-hant-tw/p/image-gallery/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://demo.stack.cai.im/p/image-gallery/helena-hertz-wWZzXlDpMog-unsplash.jpg" alt="Featured image of post 相簿" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;Stack 主題內置了對相簿的支持。你只需要簡單地將多張圖片並排放置，就可以創建一個精美的相簿。&lt;/p&gt;
